translate chinese danaq4_93bacd33:

    # cw "Do you think Mrs. Mills knows about us?"
    cw "你觉得米尔斯太太知道我们的事吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:15
translate chinese danaq4_6b67efaa:

    # pc "She hasn't said anything to me about it. Do you think she would care?"
    pc "她没跟我提过这事。你觉得她会在意吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:17
translate chinese danaq4_26c97420:

    # cw "Probably! She's so strict."
    cw "大概会吧！她那么严厉。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:18
translate chinese danaq4_e21be69c:

    # cw "She'd probably fire us both."
    cw "她八成会把我们俩都开除。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:20
translate chinese danaq4_b14300d9:

    # cw "And I can't get fired. I have rent to pay now."
    cw "但我不能被开除。我现在得交房租。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:23
translate chinese danaq4_22d4233b:

    # pc "Mrs. Mills really isn't that bad, you know?"
    pc "米尔斯太太其实没那么坏，你知道吗？"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:25
translate chinese danaq4_105e9399:

    # pc "I think she'd be a little more understanding. I don't think she'd fire us."
    pc "我觉得她应该会稍微通融一点。 我觉得她不会开除我们的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:26
translate chinese danaq4_f8826d17:

    # cw "If you say so. She's always seemed pretty mean to me."
    cw "如果你这么说的话。在我眼里她一直挺刻薄的。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:27
translate chinese danaq4_b63ff6eb:

    # pc "Oh yeah. She's mean, but she can be nice too."
    pc "哦是啊。她确实刻薄，但有时也会很和善。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:28
translate chinese danaq4_845ad89c:

    # pc "She's not all bad."
    pc "她也不是一无是处。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:30
translate chinese danaq4_3c749a81:

    # cw "Well, I'd rather she just not find out at all."
    cw "不过，我还是希望她根本别发现。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:31
translate chinese danaq4_8a1de4cc:

    # pc "Yeah, that works for me too."
    pc "是啊，我也这么想。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:34
translate chinese danaq4_6f0480be:

    # cw "Yeah, good plan."
    cw "对，好主意。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:36
translate chinese danaq4_52d7409a:

    # cw "We need to be more careful at work."
    cw "我们上班时得更小心点。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:37
translate chinese danaq4_9fe5788c:

    # cw "We've been too reckless. It's been fun, but we have to be more careful."
    cw "我们之前太鲁莽了。 虽然挺好玩的，但我们得更小心点。"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:38
translate chinese danaq4_390b4a1e:

